01:12:14,754 --> 01:12:15,274
Of course you are.

807
01:12:16,021 --> 01:12:17,241
But it's noble.

808
01:12:18,143 --> 01:12:20,256
It proves you have a conscience.

809
01:12:20,964 --> 01:12:23,071
That's why they call it "suffering equals bodhi".

810
01:12:23,868 --> 01:12:27,141
I've heard that story a lot from a church priest in prison.

811
01:12:30,685 --> 01:12:31,778
Then let me ask you.

812
01:12:32,814 --> 01:12:34,927
Do you want to be an animal?

813
01:12:36,129 --> 01:12:38,316
Or do you want to live like a human being?

814
01:12:39,193 --> 01:12:40,486
I think I'm human.

815
01:12:41,730 --> 01:12:43,210
Yeah.

816
01:12:44,407 --> 01:12:47,307
If you don't want to be an animal, you'll have to leave this village.

817
01:12:49,591 --> 01:12:50,871
You can do it.

818
01:13:17,852 --> 01:13:18,506
Kochan.

819
01:13:38,899 --> 01:13:39,993
Can't you sleep?

820
01:14:33,004 --> 01:14:35,470
Mr. Sada, how do you know a typhoon is coming?

821
01:14:36,004 --> 01:14:37,537
I can tell from the birdsong.

822
01:14:38,061 --> 01:14:39,094
You can tell from the birdsong?

823
01:14:40,180 --> 01:14:45,060
I've heard stories about predicting the weather from the morning grill.
I've never heard of bird calls.

824
01:14:45,880 --> 01:14:48,327
I can tell from the starlight.

825
01:14:48,907 --> 01:14:51,300
Because I was fisherman.

826
01:15:00,691 --> 01:15:01,417
Kochan.

827
01:15:09,322 --> 01:15:12,788
It must be hard for you.
Your husband is crippled.

828
01:15:12,813 --> 01:15:14,181
I'm used to it.

829
01:15:14,674 --> 01:15:17,067
Your business..Sada and...

830
01:15:17,214 --> 01:15:18,827
Koji works hard.

831
01:15:19,081 --> 01:15:21,934
I hear he's nice.

832
01:15:22,637 --> 01:15:24,823
I envy you.

833
01:15:25,257 --> 01:15:27,557
We all talk about you.

834
01:15:29,180 --> 01:15:31,287
The monk is worried about you.

835
01:15:32,053 --> 01:15:34,166
He worries if you don't hear anything bad

836
01:15:37,620 --> 01:15:40,294
She's here to watch our flowers.

837
01:15:40,767 --> 01:15:42,947
I'm too busy.
Bring him to take a walk today.

838
01:15:43,137 --> 01:15:46,437
Don't worry.
I will come again.

839
01:15:46,610 --> 01:15:48,470
He's used to it.

840
01:16:01,249 --> 01:16:02,389
Put him shoes on.

841
01:16:25,959 --> 01:16:26,825
Take care.

842
01:16:43,559 --> 01:16:45,359
It's hot,isn't it?

843
01:17:26,202 --> 01:17:29,349
I don't understand you.

844
01:17:30,316 --> 01:17:33,249
Why do you keep smiling like that and tormenting me and your wife?

845
01:17:36,915 --> 01:17:37,929
You hate me,right?

846
01:17:38,700 --> 01:17:40,326
Why don't you just say it out loud?

847
01:17:41,195 --> 01:17:44,808
You're willing to say what's convenient, but when it's inconvenient, you blame it on your illness and keep it deliberately vague.

848
01:17:45,628 --> 01:17:46,581
Right?

849
01:17:50,365 --> 01:17:51,371
You's making fun of me.

850
01:17:52,184 --> 01:17:53,998
 I've never seen anyone as obnoxious as you.

851
01:18:03,659 --> 01:18:06,845
You don't even want to look at me. You think I'm unforgivable, don't you?

852
01:18:07,826 --> 01:18:09,066
Right?

853
01:18:13,062 --> 01:18:13,816
Hot.

854
01:18:15,802 --> 01:18:16,696
Hot?

855
01:18:17,482 --> 01:18:18,196
It's hot.

856
01:18:19,846 --> 01:18:21,766
You're playing a monster.

857
01:18:22,547 --> 01:18:24,827
You're acting very well.

858
01:18:25,435 --> 01:18:28,408
But you know what, I'm gonna peel that monster face off your face.

859
01:18:29,863 --> 01:18:31,482
I'm getting understanding.

860
01:18:31,729 --> 01:18:35,842
Your death won't bring me and your wife together.
And as long as you're here, she and I will never be together.

861
01:18:36,525 --> 01:18:39,039
It's your conspiracy to create this weird environment.

862
01:18:40,235 --> 01:18:43,022
We can no longer kiss without guilt.

863
01:18:43,769 --> 01:18:45,756
That guilt turns the taste of a kiss to ash.

864
01:18:46,056 --> 01:18:48,816
You set us up so we'd be guilt-bound about everything.

865
01:18:49,397 --> 01:18:52,250
That's what you wanted for so long.
Revenge on us.

866
01:18:52,650 --> 01:18:53,797
Right?

867
01:18:57,213 --> 01:18:58,705
Hey listen!

868
01:18:59,525 --> 01:19:02,330
You don't have to look so serious.

869
01:19:03,588 --> 01:19:06,463
The truth is, you're happy with how you are.

870
01:19:07,205 --> 01:19:12,775
You're having a wonderful vacation, continuing the glamorous life of the past and the womanizing that has gone out of control.

871
01:19:13,564 --> 01:19:15,705
You enjoy laughing at our suffering.

872
01:19:15,986 --> 01:19:18,033
That's the laughing.

873
01:19:19,158 --> 01:19:23,220
You're trying to drag us all down into a big, dark hole with your laugh.

874
01:19:34,713 --> 01:19:36,095
What do you hate about me?

875
01:19:36,947 --> 01:19:39,408
Tell me.

876
01:19:41,134 --> 01:19:43,470
It's my fault I picked up a wrench in the hospital yard?

877
01:19:44,486 --> 01:19:46,775
I thought you left that there beforehand.

878
01:19:48,901 --> 01:19:53,597
Your plan was nearing completion when you moved into the bedroom next to mine.

879
01:19:55,097 --> 01:19:57,151
Me and your wife sleeping together in front of you.

880
01:19:57,862 --> 01:20:02,706
If I have sex with her in front of you, that's what you want.

881
01:20:03,511 --> 01:20:07,745
But I can't do that.
I don't want to become the beast you want me to be.

882
01:20:09,566 --> 01:20:13,776
She was about to be the beast but she couldn't.

883
01:20:15,651 --> 01:20:19,745
You knew this and seduced us.

884
01:20:20,831 --> 01:20:22,542
You knew there was nowhere to run, and you hunted us down.

885
01:20:23,753 --> 01:20:25,995
That's what makes this so much fun for you, isn't it?

886
01:20:28,042 --> 01:20:29,878
I’m better than you.

887
01:20:30,878 --> 01:20:35,550
I go to catch the prey, but you just wait for the prey to be hooked.

888
01:20:37,745 --> 01:20:39,066
What do you want?

889
01:20:40,323 --> 01:20:42,808
What do you really want?

890
01:20:44,003 --> 01:20:45,581
Go home.

891
01:20:45,683 --> 01:20:46,589
Go home?

892
01:20:47,050 --> 01:20:52,542
I know, I know.
But first, you're gonna tell me the truth.
Until then, I'm not letting you leave.

893
01:20:59,147 --> 01:21:00,296
I wanna die.

894
01:21:03,522 --> 01:21:05,319
You wanna die?

895
01:21:18,871 --> 01:21:20,090
What should I do?

896
01:21:20,864 --> 01:21:21,786
Tell me.

897
01:22:14,403 --> 01:22:17,270
Ko-chan.
I hope the greenhouse is okay.

898
01:22:38,104 --> 01:22:40,838
I wanna die.

899
01:22:54,288 --> 01:22:55,460
He's sleepwalking.

900
01:22:57,992 --> 01:23:02,859
Ko-chan.
He says he wants to die.

901
01:23:08,452 --> 01:23:10,186
I feel like I'm in a cave.

902
01:23:12,436 --> 01:23:15,866
It's like we're trapped in a cave with no way out.

903
01:23:20,069 --> 01:23:23,233
It was a mistake for me to come here.

904
01:23:26,241 --> 01:23:26,858
Why?

905
01:23:28,882 --> 01:23:30,092
No, you don't.

906
01:23:32,968 --> 01:23:36,991
You're holding him in your arms, and you're asking me out.

907
01:23:39,046 --> 01:23:41,249
Don't talk to me like that.

908
01:23:42,327 --> 01:23:45,764
I was just worried about you getting out of jail.

909
01:23:47,561 --> 01:23:49,218
I've had enough of those excuses.

910
01:23:50,772 --> 01:23:53,710
You've had your fun in this weird life.

911
01:23:54,210 --> 01:23:57,069
You have no intention of leaving him and escaping this darkness.

912
01:23:57,866 --> 01:24:02,718
Besides, I'm sure he'd love to see us embrace in front of his own eyes.

913
01:24:14,464 --> 01:24:19,066
I can't take it anymore.
I have to get out of here.

914
01:24:24,601 --> 01:24:29,804
I don't want to turn into a beast and chase you around.

915
01:24:46,635 --> 01:24:51,455
Are you leaving without me, Ko-chan?

916
01:24:52,924 --> 01:24:54,901
Tell me.

917
01:24:55,807 --> 01:24:57,471
Are you leaving without me?

918
01:25:01,859 --> 01:25:03,695
Don't you love me?

919
01:25:05,632 --> 01:25:08,828
We love each other.

920
01:25:09,187 --> 01:25:10,289
Was that a lie?

921
01:25:11,710 --> 01:25:13,265
You didn't love me.

922
01:25:17,994 --> 01:25:23,103
If you love me, please don't leave this house.

923
01:25:23,549 --> 01:25:26,580
I can't live without you.

924
01:25:27,510 --> 01:25:29,174
Stay like this.

925
01:25:29,199 --> 01:25:32,432
Isn't it bad?

926
01:25:32,697 --> 01:25:37,307
If I stay here, I have no choice but to die myself or kill him.

927
01:25:37,697 --> 01:25:38,838
Don't say that.

928
01:25:40,275 --> 01:25:42,393
Please.

929
01:26:33,956 --> 01:26:36,323
what are you going to do?

930
01:26:37,268 --> 01:26:39,229
I will make his wish come true.

931
01:27:17,159 --> 01:27:21,168
I ended up giving that guy what he wanted.

932
01:27:22,394 --> 01:27:28,699
Oh yeah,
He expected me to be sentenced to death.

933
01:28:11,235 --> 01:28:13,275
Thank you for coming all the way from far away.

934
01:28:13,782 --> 01:28:17,556
I am KIBE, a church worker at Sendai Prison.

935
01:28:17,853 --> 01:28:19,954
I've been expecting you.

936
01:28:29,819 --> 01:28:32,061
The bones of Koji Umemiya.

937
01:28:33,139 --> 01:28:40,350
He had no relatives, so it is a blessing that you have taken him in.

938
01:28:40,803 --> 01:28:43,116
He was a poor young man.

939
01:28:43,748 --> 01:28:46,428
I hear you've already built a grave for him.

940
01:28:46,724 --> 01:28:47,194
Yes.

941
01:28:49,155 --> 01:28:53,194
That's because Yuko asked me to do so.

942
01:28:59,155 --> 01:29:03,334
Is Yuko the girlfriend who received a life sentence?

943
01:29:03,483 --> 01:29:04,186
Yes.

944
01:29:04,694 --> 01:29:05,608
Have you met her?

945
01:29:05,818 --> 01:29:09,927
The girls are in prison in Tochigi.

946
01:29:10,045 --> 01:29:11,069
So I haven't.

947
01:29:11,358 --> 01:29:12,709
I see.

948
01:29:15,530 --> 01:29:21,803
The morning after the typhoon, I was tidying up the garden.

949
01:29:29,256 --> 01:29:32,311
It was a terrible storm.

950
01:29:33,655 --> 01:29:35,694
Your greenhouse was safe?

951
01:29:36,936 --> 01:29:38,366
No, sir. We didn't sustain any damage.

952
01:29:38,483 --> 01:29:39,577
That's good to hear.

953
01:29:40,655 --> 01:29:42,264
Are we going out together?

954
01:29:44,802 --> 01:29:46,505
My husband died last night.

955
01:29:47,154 --> 01:29:48,716
Really?

956
01:29:50,029 --> 01:29:52,880
I killed him.

957
01:29:56,349 --> 01:30:01,341
You told me that if I didn't want to become a monster, I had to leave this village.

958
01:30:03,732 --> 01:30:07,646
But I finally couldn't leave.

959
01:30:09,599 --> 01:30:13,419
And I had no choice.

960
01:30:15,122 --> 01:30:16,911
I hope you understand.

961
01:30:17,951 --> 01:30:20,935
I just want you to understand

962
01:30:24,048 --> 01:30:26,345
We're going to the police now.

963
01:30:28,111 --> 01:30:31,165
We wanted to ask you to come with us.

964
01:30:32,595 --> 01:30:39,275
When this young man was sentenced to death, Mrs. Yuko received a letter from the prison.

965
01:30:39,884 --> 01:30:45,220
She asked me to erect our three graves side by side.

966
01:30:45,993 --> 01:30:51,072
She wants to build her grave as a counterfeit while she lives.

967
01:30:51,376 --> 01:30:52,275
Yes.

968
01:30:54,118 --> 01:30:57,572
The villagers were very much against it.

969
01:30:58,892 --> 01:31:02,548
The graves of the deceased husband and wife would be enough.

970
01:31:03,298 --> 01:31:09,900
They say it would defile the cemetery to put up the grave of that young man who was guilty of murder.

971
01:31:16,163 --> 01:31:24,428
She sent me this photo asking for a grave to be built like this photo.

972
01:31:26,402 --> 01:31:30,176
Because of how pathetic her wish seemed

973
01:31:31,590 --> 01:31:38,629
When the young man was executed, I had the three of them built graves.

974
01:31:39,269 --> 01:31:44,988
As a matter of fact, Umemiya had asked me to do something about the graves before her execution.

975
01:31:46,043 --> 01:31:50,996
He knew that she wished to have their graves built.

976
01:31:51,965 --> 01:31:55,152
He asked that his grave never be built.

977
01:31:55,957 --> 01:32:01,097
I beg you not to place the three graves side by side.

978
01:32:02,277 --> 01:32:06,168
Please throw my bones into the Izu Sea.

979
01:32:07,433 --> 01:32:11,035
I ask you to smash them to pieces and scatter them in the currents of the sea.

980
01:32:13,199 --> 01:32:20,379
Umemiya didn't want to expose the traces of his cursed life to people's eyes.

981
01:32:20,637 --> 01:32:27,449
The idea of losing his remains to the sea is very typical of him.

982
01:32:27,504 --> 01:32:33,949
I was also troubled by it, since it was said by a man who is now trying to become a Buddha.

983
01:32:33,974 --> 01:32:38,457
I listened to him as he was, thinking that there was no need to disturb Umemiya's mind at this point.

984
01:32:39,090 --> 01:32:44,308
I was actually relieved when you were able to build his grave here.

985
01:32:45,387 --> 01:32:49,137
At least the Buddha cannot be happy without a grave.

986
01:32:49,324 --> 01:32:52,066
Thank you for all your hard work.

987
01:32:53,363 --> 01:32:54,324
That's it.

988
01:33:04,280 --> 01:33:06,210
Grass management is difficult.

989
01:33:07,202 --> 01:33:09,741
These are magnificent graves.

990
01:33:27,460 --> 01:33:30,835
Now the young man can go to heaven in peace.

991
01:33:31,780 --> 01:33:32,874
I will worship him.

992
01:33:33,038 --> 01:33:33,811
Please.

993
01:33:56,737 --> 01:34:07,799
THE END

